{"tid":1832904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉管有眼罩勞工手套望遠鏡　24歲土木工程師獲撤罪","createTime":"2020-01-21T13:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T13:23:32.000Z","uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2cc48dece8d9a845e484830d0786978835a63ca","tid":1832904,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200121/s00001/1579603291262/%e6%b6%89%e7%ae%a1%e6%9c%89%e7%9c%bc%e7%bd%a9%e5%8b%9e%e5%b7%a5%e6%89%8b%e5%a5%97%e6%9c%9b%e9%81%a0%e9%8f%a1-24%e6%ad%b2%e5%9c%9f%e6%9c%a8%e5%b7%a5%e7%a8%8b%e5%b8%ab%e7%8d%b2%e6%92%a4%e7%bd%aa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200121%2Fs00001%2F1579603291262%2F%25e6%25b6%2589%25e7%25ae%25a1%25e6%259c%2589%25e7%259c%25bc%25e7%25bd%25a9%25e5%258b%259e%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e6%2589%258b%25e5%25a5%2597%25e6%259c%259b%25e9%2581%25a0%25e9%258f%25a1-24%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%259c%259f%25e6%259c%25a8%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%25a8%258b%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e7%258d%25b2%25e6%2592%25a4%25e7%25bd%25aa&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6lKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=248587b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200121%2Fs00001%2F1579603291262%2F%25e6%25b6%2589%25e7%25ae%25a1%25e6%259c%2589%25e7%259c%25bc%25e7%25bd%25a9%25e5%258b%259e%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e6%2589%258b%25e5%25a5%2597%25e6%259c%259b%25e9%2581%25a0%25e9%258f%25a1-24%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%259c%259f%25e6%259c%25a8%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%25a8%258b%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e7%258d%25b2%25e6%2592%25a4%25e7%25bd%25aa&h=dbb5c971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200121/s00001/1579603291262/%e6%b6%89%e7%ae%a1%e6%9c%89%e7%9c%bc%e7%bd%a9%e5%8b%9e%e5%b7%a5%e6%89%8b%e5%a5%97%e6%9c%9b%e9%81%a0%e9%8f%a1-24%e6%ad%b2%e5%9c%9f%e6%9c%a8%e5%b7%a5%e7%a8%8b%e5%b8%ab%e7%8d%b2%e6%92%a4%e7%bd%aa</a><br />\n<br />\n網民去年11月11日發起「三罷」和「黎明行動」，全港各區均爆發警民衝突。24歲土木工程師早前被控一項管有適合作非法用途的工具罪，控方今（21日）向法庭申請撤銷控罪，工程師當場獲無罪釋放。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>報稱土木工程師的梁頌賢原被控於2019年11月11日，在摩理臣山道管有3個口罩、1個眼罩、1隻勞工手套、1卷膠紙及1個望遠鏡，並意圖作非法用途使用。案件今在東區裁判法院再提訊，控方向法庭申請撒銷控罪，梁當庭釋放。</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於同案另一被告、報稱學生的趙駿賢（22歲）原被控1項襲警及1項管有攻擊性武器，控方今申請新增在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器，以及無牌管有無線電通訊器兩罪。案件押後至3月3日再訊，以待辯方索取文件及法律意見。"},{"pid":"ebf42146c424dd9bdd5b53b1f8d414c120c3402d","tid":1832904,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"over my dead body又唔幫手告返轉頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YE6znfM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYE6znfM.gif&h=a0c5a1b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9480666777244fdcaea35facb9bba9892a59ded","tid":1832904,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ebf42146c424dd9bdd5b53b1f8d414c120c3402d","tid":1832904,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"over my dead body又唔幫手告返轉頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YE6znfM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYE6znfM.gif&h=a0c5a1b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T13:19:10.000Z","msg":"甩身先，之後先再告"},{"pid":"ab15c7bffcb804009d92883ab45d016c71c2bfaa","tid":1832904,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9480666777244fdcaea35facb9bba9892a59ded","tid":1832904,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ebf42146c424dd9bdd5b53b1f8d414c120c3402d","tid":1832904,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"over my dead body又唔幫手告返轉頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YE6znfM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYE6znfM.gif&h=a0c5a1b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T13:19:10.000Z","msg":"甩身先，之後先再告"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"好多單啦"},{"p